          }
        ],
        "methodology": "Data on the numbers of beds reported by <a href=\"https://profiles.health.ny.gov/hospital/alpha\">NY State Department of Health</a>, which was utilized in the reporting above, differs slightly from those reported by hospitals themselves. Spectator did not represent updated hospital bed numbers as a result of the COVID-19 outbreak because this data is subject to rapid change. \n\nNeighborhood and transit shapefiles were retrieved from <a href=\"https://data.cityofnewyork.us/City-Government/Neighborhood-Tabulation-Areas-NTA-/cpf4-rkhq\">NYC Open Data</a> and the <a href=\"https://www.baruch.cuny.edu/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=28016896\">GIS Lab at the Newman Library of Baruch College, CUNY</a>, respectively.\n\n<b><i>Interested in learning about how our graphics team and news reporters put this story together? Read about our process here</i></b><b>.</b>",
